                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in case of linkea overflow, lfsck reports errors about inability of handling a missed link on each run.  at the same time in the recovery mode, lfsck reports it is resolved.&lt;br/&gt;
